sentences: Buchi was born in Kaduna in 1963.
He gained admission to University of Lagos in 1983 to study English language and literary studies.
He graduated with a BA and MA in 1986 and 1988 respectively.

Buchi remained a staff member of the Department of English of the university until 1994  when he yielded to the higher calling to preach gospel of Jesus through writing and singing in the reggae music and poetry.
He started as a disc jockey in night clubs.
